      "Key": "891667CD494097BDA928D388D9466546",
      "SourceString": "Add to a weapon's Relic Slot while crafting to deal ELEMENTAL FIRE damage and use the Pyrokinesis ability. Strong against EARTH.\r\n\r\nPyrokinesis - Charge your weapon by dealing damage. When fully charged, press <keybind touch_img=\"Fireball\">Target</> to ignite a fireball and then press <keybind>Fire</> to hurl it at enemies to deal ELEMENTAL FIRE damage.",
